        "name": "Embrace the Pit",
        "type": "stat_block_section",
        "text": "Devil horns grow from your skull, and your skin takes on features of the devil responsible for your diabolic bloodline. You gain resistance 5 to fire and poison, and resistance 1 to physical damage (except silver).",
